Package: marginSVM
Type: Package
Title: Fast Spatial Refinement of Cluster Labels
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefano", family = "Cacciatore",
    email = "tkcaccia@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Refines noisy spatial cluster labels with overlapping local Nystrom
    support vector machines, graph-integrated evidence, and edge-aware total-variation
    decoding. The C++ implementation supports large two- and three-dimensional spatial
    transcriptomics datasets, multiple tissue sections, automatic overlapping tiles,
    diagnostics, and multiple CPU workers. Optional CUDA and Metal providers can
    register through a stable backend interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://tkcaccia.github.io/marginSVM/,
    https://github.com/tkcaccia/marginSVM
BugReports: https://github.com/tkcaccia/marginSVM/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
